narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you have any desire to speak French, take it.
Yes, I would recommend this class to another student if they were looking to improve their French because it helped me improve mine.
The course is relatively boring. If you have to take a language requirement, there are other better languages.
NO. Too much work. Weekly tests are MISERABLE
Great continuation of French 110. It would be stupid to take 110 and not take 120.
